Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我要到傍晚的时候才能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午纯就去叫个外卖回来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是在放暑假  不过纪还是很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到比赛了  所以一直要去参加社团训练
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棍球训练哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷的告诉你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用那个棒状的武器攻击敌人的头顶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直战斗到对方无法动弹为止的死亡游戏的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快再多看看即将面对这一切的纪的脸庞的说哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们看家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪！要加油啊！不要死！努力啊！……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！万岁！万岁——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时是从哪里找到那些书的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在那间有镜子的房间里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是德语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术和潜意识心理学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有兴趣的话你也应该可以看得懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的媒介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我共享着很多能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书中的内容自然会流入你的脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我连英文书都看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你的集中力还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个骗人的人偶！还总是这么盛气凌人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能这么简单就能被你读懂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想把人偶齐聚于这个时代\N所带来的沉重气氛转换一下的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够放松自己  她真是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会是个强大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么的说啊！什么「敌人」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶聚齐  就是爱丽丝游戏开始的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定什么时候就要必须相互战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我才不管的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然翠星石也非常喜欢父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也一样非常喜欢苍星石还有真红她们的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不得不抢夺苍星石的蔷薇圣母的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石就不想成为爱丽丝了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家永远永远在一起的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  蔷薇水晶盯上苍星石的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石一定会保护苍星石的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点找一个主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上这个走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像会下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长时间以来承蒙照顾的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我如果不去找自己的主人的话…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啊  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是永远分别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…「小不点人类」先生的家也就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  人家叫作「纯」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传染上小翠的说法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要去寻找主人  就是去纯那里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁要和纯那种家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给她上发条吗？还是不给她上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许从现在就会获得一个可爱的妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——又挂断了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  全都是不明白的人的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖的到纯那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  既然苍星石都这么说了  我就去看看的说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点人类要在厕所里躲到什么时候的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯最近总是会在厕所里看杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都很久才会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…那里确实是个漂亮的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够令人安下心来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果说看杂志的话还会是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去使劲敲厕所的门的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  你来了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实翠星石正在寻找主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？所以就来找纯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…个  那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也很喜欢纯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事的说！我才不想被卖掉的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  哼  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要高兴的滚来滚去  也就只有趁现在了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我金丝雀一定要…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先回爷爷家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的说  这样灰溜溜地逃回去也太难看了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去纯家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不愿意的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍  苍星石去拿给他的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是翠星石提出来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎么这么扭捏的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭捏的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有两把的  所以这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  既然小不点人类都找到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就逃不掉了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不和翠星石订下契约的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会放弃的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说想要和你订契约了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石才没有堕落到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要肮脏的小不点人类作主人的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要和你这种家伙订契约的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个肮脏恶心的臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…那个性格恶劣的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的纯  我不管了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇…看起来要糟糕了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是奇怪的第七人偶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然在附近出没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是计划的一大失误吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  会被那家伙先抢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我抓到了的说  你这顽固的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石在家里经常帮奶奶的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石很擅长沏烘焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是红茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷喜欢喝烘焙茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在背着人家瞎说些什么的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  稍微藏起来一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个的时候的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红她们有危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下～雨  下～雨  下～雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得雨变成果汁比较好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是变成牛奶比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…雏莓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在有镜子的房间里的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说了是水洼  怎么就是不明白呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水洼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水洼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,n之领域啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股…有点湿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你这女人想做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是蔷薇水晶的领域的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么小不点人类也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会拖后腿而已的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什么不关你们的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你们两个都没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不知怎么回事就到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  蔷薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傀儡线牵引而来的人偶们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所编织而成的是名为命运的挂毯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事的主角们现在齐集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏终于开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏样子的人偶被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种兴趣也太糟糕了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来…停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来…停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金人偶  站起来  还可以站起来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爱丽丝游戏开始了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  我们将会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！小不点莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被那种猴戏搞乱阵脚的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西和你们不是完全不同的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情不可能发生的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的爱丽丝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点糟糕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来订下契约吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之梦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了媒介在  你这种家伙根本不放在眼里的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好热啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！苍星石！要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向爷爷奶奶问好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所的电灯泡快坏了  要换一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  就是  我还会时常回去住一住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还  还有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也会来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再和我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么时候都能再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是姐妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天都要来玩的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看书的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看数学参考书？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天睡觉之前奶奶都会给我们念书的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个X乘以3之后就等于4了  所以X…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫X的很有看头的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着念下面的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…要求这个X的值以及角度…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜——！呜——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么残忍的家伙们呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜——我的屁股——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我要报复的吧——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也和纯契约了  也要住在一起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事本来是绝对会拒绝的说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没办法的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作为补偿～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓的地盘就全都归我了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快给我让开的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  早上要在我起来之前准备好我的早餐的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  比真红还难伺候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见哦
